Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years have passed\Nsince the Paramount War at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and crew returned to Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And on their way to the next stage, the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,they reached Fishman Island,\Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates are plotting to destroy Ryugu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,arm in arm with Vander Decken,\Nwho is stalking the Mermaid Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Hody Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up\Nin the turmoil little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anywhere you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a lot of places I want to go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get you out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If something's thrown at you again, I'll deflect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's formidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the sounds of a festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so I let myself out!
