Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he get out of jail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He warded off the God of the Sea, King Neptune's, attack easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you resist, we'll have casualties on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender with good grace-jamon, Zori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Rupture the bubbles\Naround them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of the Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better for us to fight them in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we've been driven to the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. This is no good. Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! All the water is gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just found a Bubbly Coral—this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,let's continue where we left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait. I'll fight him-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't bother, Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that man is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want anyone else to get hurt anymore-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hurry up and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? R-R-Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I... I mean, I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Still what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's too sudden so I still... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sort out my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you give me a little more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a walk, no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy. Don't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait so just make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you guys done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how I look at it, this is overkill!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! You should regret your actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys started this fight!\NThat means you're my accomplices, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We were gonna just intimidate them and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just enjoying sightseeing and shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's done is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's done is done"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Stopping by Fishman Island and occupying the palace\Naccidentally—what are we? Some kinda evil pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should've just\Nallowed ourselves to be beaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept telling you, we should've waited for our chance and ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the way out\Nand Luffy is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Luffy is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We really have to go\Nso don't be mean and tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, where is Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the treasure chamber?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending you're naive! Be sensible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're sad, let's sing and be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be alright! It's gonna be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not, you're gonna die\Nsomeday anyway, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already, Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that this is happening\Nto King Neptune, the Great Knight of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fight when I've thrown out my back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I got old...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault-jamon. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've broken their bubbles\Nand made them fight in the water earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we let them drain all the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When the three princes of the Neptune Army—\NFukaboshi, Ryuboshi, Manboshi—come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we can't stay here on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Sunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get everyone together and set sail as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the coating on the Sunny came off\Nwhen we entered the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Log Pose hasn't been\Nworking right for a while either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been unstable since we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it! That Pose is not good enough\Nto sail across the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You ignorant pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This is not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you if you untie me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Prince Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is odd. What are the guards doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Ryuboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Manboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think—Brother—something is going on-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree! Are Father and Shirahoshi alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Fukaboshi. What is going on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower the gate immediately and let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be honest and tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah guys, tie me and Camie up too! They'll think we're your accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro-chin's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(0,1750)}Prince Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(0,1750)}Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:51.36,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(0,1750)}Prince Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:51.36,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(0,1750)}Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a member of the Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukaboshi! That's the Three-Sword Style\Nswordsman of the Straw Hats—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Hunter Zori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have Father too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you just heard,\Nwe have Neptune and many other hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want me to kill them,\Nprepare for us to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need is our ship,\Nthe Sunny, re-coated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know where it is so go find it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the rest of our crew, a gloomy woman,\Na robot, a raccoon dog, and a dirty water imp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And Zoro, one billion berries in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dirty water imp"... That's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dirty water imp"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What about "gloomy woman"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make arrangements for you to leave this country\Nwith all of your crewmates immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want all the hostages back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This gateway is the only way\Nto enter Ryugu Palace, even for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to break in elsewhere\Nsince it's covered in several layers of bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one more thing. Zoro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't normally tell you this\Nunder these circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't ignore my duty to Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from the former Warlord, \NFirst Son of the Sea Jinbe. to Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He left two messages for me\Nto give to you when you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.65,Alt,,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.95,Alt,,0,0,0,,Jinbe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy said that he became friends with Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he was in the newspaper with Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he's a pirate, he's a big figure\Nthat people on the island trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy's not here but I'll tell him later. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,First, he says to not fight against Hody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, he'll be waiting at the Sea Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want you to find the Straw Hats' ship and the rest of the crew as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.23,Alt,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hat Pirates really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They took over Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! They looked like really good people—\NI can't believe they'd do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I bet they're the ones who kidnapped the Mermaids\Nand the prediction's right about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how things are progressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally showed their true colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the two of them are hiding in the back of the Mermaid Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Guards are heading there to catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kung Fu Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji just got better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come to Ryugu Palace"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to catch us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, you should still be in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I can't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You said there's places you wanna go, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I do something like that, it's going to cause a lot of trouble for everybody in the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stayed in here for ten years, I'd go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in return for the food—I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The S—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it's just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do such a selfish thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying\Njust from saying where you wanna go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry. It's because I summoned\Nall my courage to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't get mad!\NYou are scaring me, Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pain in the butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? That was so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he throwing something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rude guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this noise-jamon?\NDon't tell me it's Decken again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from Hard Shell Tower-jamon!\NShirahoshi must be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there guards with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're all tied up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pirates! Go see if the Princess is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama! They'll find out about the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard Shell Tower is on the northeast side\Nof the palace! You guys, go there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we being ordered around by our hostages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! Shirahoshi is my only daughter-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody is trying to kill her day in, day out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happens to my daughter,\NI'll shove you all off the end of an ocean trench!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So she is {\i1}the{\i0} Mermaid Princess, am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go there as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,can I ask her to show me her panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't take it!\NHe's heading there with lascivious intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's in a different kind of danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to untie me but take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have jurisdiction over the tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happened to the Princess, I would be beside myself with regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wanna see her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How lecherous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san, excuse me for seeing her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to go to the Sea Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For these ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But everybody is kind enough to tell me\Nthat it's too dangerous to go out of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am scared of going out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, are you really going to take me out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Count on me! You're gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, I'm not gonna take you if you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, to be accurate,\Nyou have to take me since I can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am so sorry. I am too delighted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a crybaby, huh? And a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But once you go out,\Neverybody will recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Princess?! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Skeleton! Look at the tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!\NThose aren't knives or axes like usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the sound\Nof human pirates hitting the tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How eccentric! He's not normal,\Nthat man—Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! V-Vander Decken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is no good!\NThey're getting on their feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean the impregnable Ryugu Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,has been invaded by enemy forces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a surprise attack! The King is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The attack stopped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Wimpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! We are ready, Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Megalo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Sea Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shirahoshi is discovered missing, Ryugu Palace is thrown into a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, a group of unknown pirates\Nhave infiltrated the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These pirates seem driven to attack\Nthe Straw Hats at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in Coral Hill, a critically wounded Hachi\Nappears before Sanji and Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ryugu Palace in Shock!\NThe Shirahoshi Kidnapping Incident"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.91,0:23:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
